/header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dpa1665702875291.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dpa1665702875291.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dpa1665702875291.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dpa1665702875291\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Restrictions on Use of Unicode and Installable Character Sets\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__restrictions_on_use_of_unicode_and_installable_character_sets_93370\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Although Uniface supports Unicode and the installable character sets, there are restrictions in using them.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__p_d28571e1_d28572e1_d28573e1\">ASCII characters are allowed anywhere.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__p_d28574e1_d28575e1_d28576e1\">The following tables show where the full Unicode character set (as opposed to the BMP), and the installable character set can be used.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Unicode Support in the Development Objects</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n Object\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n Full Range Unicode\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Installable Character Set\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n Model, entity and field names.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n All other object names, such as form names.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n No\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n Entity abbreviation\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n No\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n Component subtype\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n No\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Description</span> property of all objects\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Comments</span> property of all objects\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n Yes\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n ProcScript\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n Yes\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n Labels\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n Yes\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">Menu items</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__2\">\n Yes\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__3\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dpa1665702875291__table_d2942e1_d2943e1_d2944e1__entry__1\">\n ValRep pairs in widgets\n </t